flowchart TD
  subgraph RegistrationTransaction
    R1[Begin Prisma transaction] --> R2[Create user]
    R2 --> R3[Create default categories]
    R3 --> R4[Generate token pair]
    R4 --> R5[Store refresh token digest]
    R5 --> R6[Commit]
    R2 -. failure .-> RR[Rollback]
    R3 -. failure .-> RR
    R5 -. failure .-> RR
  end

  subgraph TransactionCreate
    C1[Begin Prisma transaction] --> C2[Find category by userId and categoryId]
    C2 --> C3{Category exists and type matches?}
    C3 -->|yes| C4[Create transaction]
    C4 --> C5[Commit]
    C3 -->|no| CR[Rollback and TRANSACTION_CATEGORY_INVALID]
  end

  subgraph TransactionUpdate
    U1[Begin Prisma transaction] --> U2[Find transaction by userId and id]
    U2 --> U3{Transaction exists?}
    U3 -->|yes| U4[Derive next category and type]
    U4 --> U5[Validate category ownership and type]
    U5 --> U6[Update transaction]
    U6 --> U7[Commit]
    U3 -->|no| UR[Rollback and TRANSACTION_NOT_FOUND]
  end
